name: Arcane Symbol: Vanishing Journey
description:
The Arcane Symbol from the #cVanishing Journey# area. It contains Arcane Power that #cincreases the main stat# of whoever possesses it. 
Equip this Arcane Symbol and feed it duplicates from your inventory by #cdouble-clicking# them to grant it experience.
Stat boosts granted by the Arcane Symbol are not affected by % stat boosts.
